<C>__{a doctor}
<P>__{(listening to his heartbeat)}
<D>__{the heart is going to stop! the stimulator, quickly.}
<A>__{suddenly, everything collapses for jacques. sounds disappear. the image slows down, the light fades. jacques only hears his heartbeat, which slows down. his heart stops. among the crowd around him, he sees johana, fresh, gentle, smiling. her movements are smooth and slowed down. she smiles at him, simply. jacques smiles back. the heart starts again slowly. the image goes back to normal. sounds multiply (doctors, the panic, etc...) and slowly come back. jacques falls unconscious.}
